^B@2^*BHoward: ^*N|cp||at|A negative  double is not recommended. I think a VERY important  bidding principle is, you must show support with support immediately with 4+ card support. If you do not raise partner immediately, you cannot have 4-card support. I don't care if you are 7-4, raise partner, don't bid your 7-card suit. That might be a slight exaggeration, but I am trying to make an important point here.|
